26
00:01:07,103 --> 00:01:09,972
Ten klavirista, čo zomrel...

27
00:01:10,442 --> 00:01:11,442
bol v skutočnosti...

28
00:01:12,142 --> 00:01:13,513
môj syn.

29
00:01:15,342 --> 00:01:17,153
Váš syn?

30
00:01:17,312 --> 00:01:18,353
Áno.

31
00:01:19,952 --> 00:01:21,582
Po rozvode odišiel s mamou...

32
00:01:22,222 --> 00:01:24,023
