a potom ma obviňuj.

94
00:04:42,992 --> 00:04:45,752
Nemal ten dôkaz Yoon Young Gil?

95
00:04:47,023 --> 00:04:48,362
Vravíš, že som zabil 
Yoon Young Gila...

96
00:04:48,362 --> 00:04:50,262
