97
00:04:51,663 --> 00:04:53,233
Nepamätám si presné slová...

98
00:04:53,762 --> 00:04:55,262
ale v strede videa...

99
00:04:55,762 --> 00:04:57,333
ste sa profesora spýtali...

100
00:04:57,533 --> 00:04:59,502
či zabil Yoon Young Gila preto...

101
00:04:59,502 --> 00:05:02,343
že mal dôkaz o tom, 
že zabil Kim Iana.

102
00:05:04,213 --> 00:05:05,273
Naozaj?

103
00:05:05,473 --> 00:05:06,812
Nepovedali ste to?

104
00:05:07,413 --> 00:05:09,012
Vôbec si na to nespomínam.

105
00:05:09,012 --> 00:05:11,052
Podľa mňa ste vy, profesor Kang...

106
00:05:11,052 --> 00:05:12,382
Yoon Young Gil a Kim Ian...

107
00:05:13,283 --> 00:05:14,922
všetci nejak prepojení.

108
00:05:16,353 --> 00:05:19,192
Bol pán Yoon naozaj 
len váš fanúšik?

109
00:05:20,922 --> 00:05:21,922
Áno.

110
00:05:22,562 --> 00:05:24,163
Nič viac, nič menej.

111
00:05:35,672 --> 00:05:37,812
Viete, na ktorých schodoch 
zomrel Yoon Young Gil?

112
00:05:38,372 --> 00:05:39,572
Hľadali ste ho aj...

113
00:05:40,112 --> 00:05:42,742
pri núdzovom východe, 
čo je pri schodisku?

114
00:05:43,413 --> 00:05:44,713
Nie, ja...

115
00:05:46,213 --> 00:05:47,752
Na tú stranu som nešla.

116
00:06:14,143 --> 00:06:15,182
Slečna Yang.

117
00:06:20,182 --> 00:06:21,223
Prečo predo mnou utekáte?

118
00:06:21,223 --> 00:06:22,283
Neutekám.

119
00:06:22,583 --> 00:06:24,622
Otočili ste sa hneď, 
ako ste ma zbadali.

120
00:06:24,622 --> 00:06:25,992
Nie.

121
00:06:25,992 --> 00:06:28,163
No tak, nepopierajte to...

122
00:06:28,163 --> 00:06:29,393
