123
00:06:29,963 --> 00:06:31,333
Nie som Yu Da.

124
00:06:31,333 --> 00:06:32,762
- Uhnite. 
- Dobre, dobre.

125
00:06:32,893 --> 00:06:34,062
Povedzme, že nie ste Yu Da.

126
00:06:36,672 --> 00:06:37,703
Jedli ste?

127
00:06:38,572 --> 00:06:39,572
Čože?

128
00:06:40,502 --> 00:06:41,672
Nezájdeme spolu na obed?

129
00:06:42,903 --> 00:06:43,973
Nie.

130
00:06:45,072 --> 00:06:46,512
Čo máte najradšej?

131
00:06:55,953 --> 00:06:56,992
Kam ste išli pred koncertom...

132
00:06:57,422 --> 00:06:59,453
