133
00:06:59,723 --> 00:07:01,062
Nepamätám si to.

134
00:07:01,422 --> 00:07:02,822
Nevzdávajte sa tak ľahko.

135
00:07:03,062 --> 00:07:04,533
Skúste si spomenúť.

136
00:07:04,733 --> 00:07:06,762
Jasne ste si predsa pamätali...

137
00:07:06,903 --> 00:07:08,932
